      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. Powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system, this unit delivers linear power to a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and retains its factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. With an unblemished Carbon Black finish and a pristine Nappa leather interior, this vehicle represents a mechanically optimized, collector-tier example of Bavarian engineering.",
