      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in breathtaking showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector-grade example that must be seen to be fully appreciated. The exterior features a flawless, deep-luster paint finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring a mirror-like shine with absolutely no swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium hand-stitched leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive, documented maintenance history included. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model. The sale includes both original keys, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker.",
